Andale, pues...

118
00:09:38,245 --> 00:09:40,706
estoy listo...

119
00:10:20,037 --> 00:10:23,123
That doesn't
surprise me.

120
00:10:23,207 --> 00:10:25,459
It should at least
concern you.

121
