Thank you.

126
00:10:45,395 --> 00:10:49,775
Listen, you pay me
to counsel you,

127
00:10:49,858 --> 00:10:51,693
and I am counseling you.

128
00:10:51,735 --> 00:10:54,905
I'm keeping you alive
with information.

129
00:10:54,947 --> 00:10:56,782
If you disregard
my counsel

130
