John, what do you want,
toast or--

150
00:11:59,136 --> 00:12:01,597
Waffles!

151
00:12:02,723 --> 00:12:03,724
Anybody seen
my keys?

152
00:12:07,769 --> 00:12:08,812
Pancakes!

153
00:12:08,854 --> 00:12:09,771
Toast, please.

154
00:12:10,772 --> 00:12:12,983
Bye, Dad!

155
00:12:13,066 --> 00:12:14,526
Bye, pal.

156
00:12:14,610 --> 00:12:16,195
Hello. Yes.

157
