what's going on.

180
00:13:22,469 --> 00:13:23,971
I need you there.

181
00:13:24,054 --> 00:13:24,972
Where?

182
00:13:25,097 --> 00:13:27,850
In my office,
doing my job.

183
00:13:27,891 --> 00:13:29,351
Oh, wait. I--

184
00:13:29,434 --> 00:13:32,187
I hate not knowing
what's going on, Jack.

185
00:13:32,271 --> 00:13:34,857
I wouldn't know
anything about your job.

186
00:13:34,940 --> 00:13:37,776
You've been around.
No big mystery.

187
00:13:37,818 --> 00:13:39,486
You've been to
the White House.

188
00:13:39,528 --> 00:13:41,613
Once. I hated it.

189
00:13:41,697 --> 00:13:43,866
No, you didn't.

190
00:13:43,866 --> 00:13:45,409
Want to know
about politics

191
