201
00:14:10,434 --> 00:14:12,311
Get him up to speed

202
00:14:12,394 --> 00:14:15,314
on our aid program
to the Colombians.

203
00:14:15,439 --> 00:14:18,233
He's got to talk
the Oversight Committee

204
00:14:18,317 --> 00:14:20,110
