$75 million.

205
00:14:20,235 --> 00:14:23,405
And not make a fool
out of himself.

206
00:14:23,488 --> 00:14:25,782
What's happening on
the Hardin murders?

207
00:14:25,866 --> 00:14:27,201
I'm on it.

208
00:14:27,242 --> 00:14:30,829
