210
00:14:33,874 --> 00:14:36,919
That's great.

211
00:14:52,184 --> 00:14:53,310
Margaret.

212
00:14:53,352 --> 00:14:56,188
Why don't we leave
all his things?

213
00:14:56,271 --> 00:14:58,023
O.K.

214
00:15:09,952 --> 00:15:13,121
Ryan...
I can't believe it!

215
00:15:13,205 --> 00:15:14,581
Not a team player,

216
00:15:14,665 --> 00:15:16,625
