Believes in loyalty,
cleanliness, and knot tying.

220
00:15:24,299 --> 00:15:26,593
So leave him
out of it.

221
00:15:26,677 --> 00:15:28,053
He's the Deputy
Director

222
00:15:28,136 --> 00:15:29,513
of lntelligence,
James.

223
00:15:29,596 --> 00:15:32,349
