a little tricky.

224
00:15:32,432 --> 00:15:34,768
What does he
need to know?

225
00:15:34,852 --> 00:15:35,727
Nothing.

226
00:15:35,811 --> 00:15:37,646
He needs
to know nothing.

227
00:15:37,729 --> 00:15:39,523
He's going to know
nothing.

228
00:15:39,606 --> 00:15:40,983
I want a copy

229
00:15:41,066 --> 00:15:42,401
of the President's
authorization

230
00:15:42,484 --> 00:15:43,861
of this
new action

231
00:15:43,944 --> 00:15:45,320
against
the cartels.

232
00:15:47,197 --> 00:15:49,074
You want what?

233
00:15:49,157 --> 00:15:50,576
You heard me.

234
00:15:52,035 --> 00:15:53,203
He doesn't know
about it.

235
00:15:55,372 --> 00:15:57,875
Let me explain it
to you very simply.

236
00:15:57,958 --> 00:15:59,710
This is your deal,

237
00:15:59,751 --> 00:16:01,461
not mine.

238
00:16:01,503 --> 00:16:04,423
So unless I have
written authorization,

239
00:16:04,506 --> 00:16:06,466
